I"q<p>Matt Shifrin is a blind high school student. In 2016, he created a system for blind and visually impaired people to build Lego sets.</p>

<p>My friend Sharon introduced me to Matt later that year; I was impressed by his creativity and ambition. We teamed up to bring Lego for the Blind to a greater audience.</p>

